ZCODE BOLD START--><b> Rules for Flawless Victory on Ozma</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>- No characters killed (at all)  - *most important*<br>- No status effects on characters by time fight is over<br>- ALL items that can be stolen were stolen<br>- NO CHEATS (eg. GameShark) - tied for 1st requirement in most important<br><br>If you did not make it a Flawless Victory, how close did you come? I mean to detail ...Eg. such as, you followed all the rules but you couldn't steal that Pumice Piece.<br><br>If you did make a Flawless Victory - how? Do you think luck was the key factor? What level were your characters?<br><br><br>Yes, I am a bit of a perfectionist. You do not want to know what my playtime hours is up to... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :| --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/indifferent.gif ALT=":|"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">  <tr>    <td width="100%" colspan="3"><img border="0" src="http://shenlung.20m.com/sig04.jpg" width="490" height="125"></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td width="33%" bgcolor="#808080">      <p align="right"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Chuka Tonglong</font></p>    </td>    <td width="33%" bgcolor="#808080">      <p align="center"><font face="Arial" color="#EAD6B0" size="1">Brell Serilis</font></p>    </td>    <td width="34%" bgcolor="#808080"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">Shenlung Tianzhu</font></td>  </tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm40.showPrevMessage?topicID=305.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm40.showNextMessage?topicID=305.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=305.top